      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "PLATINUM ZEAL (1) showed blistering pace early and gave a sight when in the minors, beaten 2.25 lengths over 388m this track in 22.55. Has performed well from this box with a win and five minor placings to his name from 10 starts. Good form should continue. SILENT MINUTE (8) is a handy dog who jumped from box 8 last time out and scored by 1.5 lengths at this track (22.29). Safe beginner but wide box to overcome and will need some luck. One of the key runners again. MY HARLEY (3) had a tricky draw and ran well to finish second, beaten 1.5 lengths, (22.40) at this track. Yet to win out of this box but has been in the placings three times from five starts. Expecting another good run. MOLLIE'S MAID (2) cannot be left out after placing here at this trip last start.",
